transcript:
Customer: Aapne jis vyakti ko call kiya hai, woh abhi dusre call par vyast hai. Kripya pratiksha kare ya kuch samay pashchat prayas kare. The person you have called is speaking to someone else. You can wait or call again later.
Customer: Aapne jis vyakti ko call kiya hai, woh abhi dusre call par vyast hai. Kripya pratiksha kare ya kuch
Customer: Aap jis vyakti se baat
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hanji sir.
Executive: Hello.
Executive: Haan good morning boliye.
Customer: Sir maine na aapko video meeting ki link bheji hai ek bari join kijiyega please.
Executive: Yeh mere sath na Avyukt sahab bhi line pe hai.
Customer: Hanji.
Executive: Amit bhai line pe hai.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan haan haan ji Amit ji Amit ji kya kar rahe ho?
Customer: Nahi mai Roshan baat kar raha hu.
Executive: Achha achha Roshan ji. Roshan ji bataiye.
Customer: Sir namaste kaise ho aap?
Executive: Bas dua hai sir aapki.
Customer: Sir maine na video meeting ki link bheji hui hai.
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Ek baar ko join kariyega sir.
Executive: Mujhe par bataiye ki resolve hua ki nahi hua abhi.
Customer: Sir usi cheez ke regarding me maine aapko fir share kara hua hai. Team wale hi connect karenge. Jo is looking for this na.
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: Wahi connect karenge. Unhone hi bola video meeting arrange karane ko.
Executive: Matlab abhi tak resolve nahi hua.
Customer: Sir mai wahi check karne ke liye hi maine aapko call kara hua hai. Sir please aap mujhe yeh dijiye thoda time mai usi cheez ke liye maine khud se call kara aapko.
Executive: Maine aapko whatsapp pe bheja hai na sir link.
Executive: Hmm.
Executive: Google meet ka.
Customer: Haan.
Customer: Mai unko bhi join karne ko bolta hu ek second line pe rukiyega.
Executive: Tareekh kar chuke.
Executive: Tareekh bhai aap kar lo meeting attend, theek hai?
Customer: Theek hai, mere ko batana aap.

Customer: Hello Vikas ji Roshan baat kar raha hu.
Customer: Woh meeting join kar lijiye maine link share kara aapko.
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai.
Customer: Sir aapne join kara?
Customer: Haan apni screen share kar dijiye please.
Customer: Ankita samajh nahi aa raha hai kya?
Customer: Apni screen share kar dijiye sir us din jaise kiya tha na aapne.
Customer: Woh niche me three dot pe click kijiye haan haan aap.

Customer: Haan.
Customer: Vikas ji please take over.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai theek hai theek hai haan sir ek baar aap.
